Please, no hit and runners! Try to seed at least 150%. If possible, do not stop seeding until three (3) seeds or more exists on  the torrent.

If anyone's curious, you can also get C64 albums, for free, in MP3 format from Galbadia Hotel. The site is back up and I suggest that any self-respecting VGM (video game music) fan picks up this stuff while they still can.
Thanks for the cover art though, couldn't find it anywhere else. ^_^
